Hi Everyone,
Greetings from India. I am a Rajput but when ever i hear this i feel it connects me with my Shree Ram Ji. Such is the power of music that it connect every human with any religion to their God. Pakistan is blessed with  numerous talent in all the field. I wish i can witness these things there by visiting. I hope my wish will be granted someday. Lots of Love and respect to all my Pakistani Brothers and sisters. By the way i have broken my replay button :).
